# API base for the dashboard frontend.
#
# Leave UNSET for the primary deployment: the static export is served by
# the Replit FastAPI server at /dashboard, so the API is same-origin and
# requests stay relative (/api/*). `npm run dev` auto-targets :8080.
#
# Set this ONLY for a separate host (e.g. a standalone Vercel deploy):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://beezy-agents-ingestion.replit.app
